    <question number="199">
        <prompt>What was the main effect of Frederick Winslow Taylor's ideas?</prompt>
        <options>
            <option letter="a">They increased industrial efficiency while reducing worker autonomy</option>
            <option letter="b">They improved working conditions</option>
            <option letter="c">They strengthened unions</option>
            <option letter="d">They increased wages</option>
        </options>
        <answer>a</answer>
        <explanation>Taylor's scientific management principles increased industrial efficiency but reduced worker autonomy by breaking tasks into standardized, measured components.</explanation>
    </question>
